concepts.term: T-E should always be less than T-R

evidence: After the first sequence, you can wait for a time T-R, and then repeat the same trick... But in order for the system to be in a stable state, T-R has to be long enough so that the magnetization vector M-naught has fully recovered.
triples.o: full recovery of the longitudinal magnetization vector M-naught
